{"sn2.27:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.27 ","sn2.27:0.2":"3. Nanatitthiyavagga ","sn2.27:0.3":"Nandasutta ","sn2.27:1.1":"Ekamantam thito kho nando devaputto bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn2.27:2.1":"“Accenti kala tarayanti rattiyo, ","sn2.27:2.2":"Vayoguna anupubbam jahanti; ","sn2.27:2.3":"Etam bhayam marane pekkhamano, ","sn2.27:2.4":"Punnani kayiratha sukhavahani”ti. ","sn2.27:3.1":"“Accenti kala tarayanti rattiyo, ","sn2.27:3.2":"Vayoguna anupubbam jahanti; ","sn2.27:3.3":"Etam bhayam marane pekkhamano, ","sn2.27:3.4":"Lokamisam pajahe santipekkho”ti. "}